                                </div>
                                <p class="section-title">처리 가능 여부 체크</p>
                                <table class="data-table mb-4">
                                    <thead><tr><th>확인항목</th><th>확인값</th><th>결과</th><th>비고</th></tr></thead>
                                    <tbody>
                                        <tr><td class="font-bold">신고수리 완료 여부</td><td>수리완료</td><td><span class="badge-done">정상</span></td><td>수리일 2026-04-12</td></tr>
                                        <tr><td class="font-bold">세금 납부 여부</td><td>납부완료</td><td><span class="badge-done">정상</span></td><td>납부금액 1,240,000원</td></tr>
