                                        <tr><td class="font-bold">보세구역 반입 여부</td><td>반입완료</td><td><span class="badge-done">정상</span></td><td>냉동A구역 반입 2026-04-12</td></tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                                <p class="section-title">반출 정보</p>
